<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Best Blog Site</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="background-wrapper">
      <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
      <div class="blob blob-2"></div>
      <div class="blob blob-3"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-container">
      <nav class="navbar">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/posts">Posts</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="active">About us</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <main class="about-section">
        <div class="about-header">
          <h2 class="page-title">Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="about-lead">
            We are a community of thinkers, writers, and dreamers. Our goal is
            to provide a space where ideas can flow freely and knowledge is
            shared without boundaries.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">🚀</div>
            <h3>Innovation</h3>
            <p>Always looking for the next big idea to change the world.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">🌍</div>
            <h3>Community</h3>
            <p>Connecting people from different backgrounds through words.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="icon">💡</div>
            <h3>Creativity</h3>
            <p>Express yourself authentically and artistically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="story-section">
          <h3>Our Story</h3>
          <p>
            Started in 2026, Best Blog Site began as a small project to help
            developers learn backend programming. Today, it stands as a
            testament to the power of code and design coming together. We
            believe that every line of code tells a story, and every story
            deserves to be heard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </main>

      <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
